title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Sep 30 2022

description:
A Vermont high school has shut down the locker room after girls on the volleyball team complained about having to share the locker room with a biological man identifying as a transgender woman. Buck's engagement party. Author Ann Coulter in-studio with Clay and Buck to give us her one-of-a-kind take on the midterms. Pelosi: Let Martha's Vineyard illegals pick crops.
